title: Ariana Grande unveils new snippet of 'Focus'
text: Ariana Grande unveils new snippet of 'Focus' Friday, 23 October 2015 (12 minutes ago) Los Angeles, Oct 23 : Another preview of Ariana Grande's "Focus" has landed online a little over a week before the single's release date. The singer shares an Instagram clip featuring her belting out some lines from her new single, which will finally arrive in full on October 30. AceShowbiz 19 hours ago - Entertainment The singer features a snippet of the song in the newly-released ad for her 'Ari by *Ariana Grande*' fragrance.
